 match those expected from the asteroseismic Survey\nPhase of Kepler show that it will be possible to infer stellar radii\nsuccessfully using our method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2009 20:00:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
