ared to the case without bulk flows for realistic\nvelocities). Our results reiterate that high-resolution Eulerian methods can\nperform well and obtain a convergent solution, even in the presence of highly\nsupersonic bulk flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2009 20:12:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2009 04:34:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-03"}
