 Lifshitz transition and correlation effects.\nWe discuss common underlying physics in these examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2009 02:19:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Aug 2010 07:50:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-08-24"}
